local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["whereby"]={"whereby","[weə'baɪ]","[wɛr'bai]","adv.借此",'adv.借此(在...旁,凭什么)','The process whereby a digital computer translates the instructions of a program written in a high-level language into their machine language equivalents.','数字计算机借此把高级语言编写的程序中的指令翻译成与其等价的机器语言程序的处理过程。','He devised a plan whereby he might escape.','他想出了一个可藉以逃脱的办法。'}
